1
00:01:14,040 --> 00:01:15,239
If she doesn't wake up,

2
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:16,840
even if I die,

3
00:01:16,879 --> 00:01:18,000
I'll take you with me!

4
00:01:18,040 --> 00:01:18,760
Don't worry,

5
00:01:19,599 --> 00:01:20,480
she'll be fine.

6
00:01:20,920 --> 00:01:22,120
With your ability?

7
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:26,000
How much do you really know about her?

8
00:01:27,760 --> 00:01:29,120
Do you know she has a hematologic disease?

9
00:01:29,560 --> 00:01:31,120
Excessive blood loss can be fatal!

10
00:01:34,000 --> 00:01:35,920
Moon grew up by my side.

11
00:01:37,959 --> 00:01:38,879
When she fell,

12
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:40,159
or got into fights,

13
00:01:40,719 --> 00:01:41,920
I always helped her.

14
00:01:43,959 --> 00:01:45,719
When she was 18, she told me

15
00:01:46,799 --> 00:01:48,840
since life could end at any moment,

16
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:50,680
she might as well go far away

17
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,439
and explore the wild.

18
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,200
She was really willful.

19
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,239
You don't understand her.

20
00:01:59,799 --> 00:02:01,959
Even if a little beast is kept in a cage,

21
00:02:02,920 --> 00:02:03,840
it won't be happy

22
00:02:04,480 --> 00:02:05,519
without freedom.

23
00:02:05,560 --> 00:02:06,280
Yes,

24
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,000
I'm a control freak,

25
00:02:10,159 --> 00:02:11,879
boring and annoying brother.

26
00:02:13,599 --> 00:02:15,199
She changed her major without telling me,

27
00:02:15,719 --> 00:02:17,319
and went on adventures all over the world.

28
00:02:18,919 --> 00:02:20,000
The Amazon rainforest,

29
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:22,000
mountains, and Antarctica.

30
00:02:22,800 --> 00:02:24,120
She thought I wouldn't know.

31
00:02:26,080 --> 00:02:28,360
If I hadn't been deceiving myself

32
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,319
and covering for her,

33
00:02:29,960 --> 00:02:31,680
do you think she could have fooled

34
00:02:31,840 --> 00:02:32,919
my father with her little tricks?

35
00:02:38,039 --> 00:02:39,520
Jiang Yue doesn't dislike you.

36
00:02:41,240 --> 00:02:43,439
She cares deeply about the bond between you.

37
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:49,840
Kinship?

38
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:53,120
Ridiculous.

39
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:56,080
I'm not her real brother.

40
00:02:59,360 --> 00:03:00,080
Lu Zhiyu,

41
00:03:02,000 --> 00:03:03,639
we are both not good people.

42
00:03:04,680 --> 00:03:05,840
Let's see

43
00:03:08,000 --> 00:03:10,120
who will go to hell first.

44
00:03:18,080 --> 00:03:19,039
It seems that

45
00:03:20,360 --> 00:03:21,319
I failed to save you this time.

46
00:03:22,319 --> 00:03:23,120
I'm so cold.

47
00:03:26,520 --> 00:03:27,240
You are injured.

48
00:03:28,159 --> 00:03:28,879
You are bleeding.

49
00:03:34,719 --> 00:03:35,680
Will I die?

50
00:03:37,159 --> 00:03:38,639
With Zang Feng by your side,

51
00:03:39,719 --> 00:03:40,759
you won't die.

52
00:03:45,759 --> 00:03:46,560
Suddenly,

53
00:03:47,159 --> 00:03:48,719
it seems to have warmed up.

54
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,039
He's using his blood to save you,

55
00:03:53,599 --> 00:03:55,120
just like he saved me back then.

56
00:03:56,199 --> 00:03:56,960
What did you say?

57
00:03:57,919 --> 00:03:59,479
I was born with vaginal atresia.

58
00:04:00,280 --> 00:04:01,919
My father feared I couldn't marry,

59
00:04:02,080 --> 00:04:03,319
which would tarnish the family's reputation.

60
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:06,000
He turned to a witch doctor,

61
00:04:07,000 --> 00:04:08,400
to keep me alive

62
00:04:09,560 --> 00:04:10,479
with wolf blood.

63
00:04:13,800 --> 00:04:15,240
So Cang Feng

64
00:04:15,879 --> 00:04:17,680
thinks he's strong

65
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:20,000
and can never run out of blood.

66
00:04:20,680 --> 00:04:21,879
That's because he's naive,

67
00:04:22,399 --> 00:04:23,000
loyal,

68
00:04:24,000 --> 00:04:25,319
and willing to give you everything.

69
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:26,879
So,

70
00:04:27,319 --> 00:04:28,600
after you found out the truth,

71
00:04:28,800 --> 00:04:30,120
to save his life,

72
00:04:31,279 --> 00:04:32,360
you let him go on purpose.

73
00:04:33,240 --> 00:04:34,439
The whole mansion thought

74
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:36,720
I became cruel and vicious

75
00:04:37,199 --> 00:04:38,879
because I drank wolf blood.

76
00:04:40,519 --> 00:04:43,000
In fact, I was tired of their hypocrisy.

77
00:04:44,800 --> 00:04:46,160
They pretended to love me,

78
00:04:47,519 --> 00:04:49,680
but they actually wanted to marry me off

79
00:04:49,759 --> 00:04:51,240
to gain wealth and status.

80
00:04:52,279 --> 00:04:53,240
Only my mother

81
00:04:54,240 --> 00:04:55,560
couldn't bear to see me become a monster

82
00:04:56,120 --> 00:04:57,160
and tried hard to stop it.

83
00:04:57,720 --> 00:04:58,720
But not long after,

84
00:04:59,279 --> 00:05:01,120
she died of madness.

85
00:05:03,439 --> 00:05:05,480
From then on, the entire household fell silent.

86
00:05:07,480 --> 00:05:08,720
They raised me, this gu worm.

87
00:05:11,360 --> 00:05:12,079
So,

88
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:15,040
you don't want to drain his blood for the rest of your life,

89
00:05:16,720 --> 00:05:18,199
and would rather let him hate you?

90
00:05:19,279 --> 00:05:20,519
If it were you, Jiang Yue,

91
00:05:21,279 --> 00:05:23,040
would you rather die quickly

92
00:05:24,720 --> 00:05:26,319
or live with heavy sins?

93
00:05:30,319 --> 00:05:30,879
You go.

94
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,000
Tell him the whole truth.

95
00:05:35,279 --> 00:05:36,800
I don't need anyone's pity.

96
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,759
This is between the two of us,

97
00:05:41,600 --> 00:05:42,680
and me.

98
00:05:43,759 --> 00:05:44,920
You are my new life.

99
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:46,879
You don't have to dwell on the past.

100
00:05:48,040 --> 00:05:49,279
As for Cang Feng,

101
00:05:50,839 --> 00:05:52,439
his heart has been healed,

102
00:05:54,120 --> 00:05:55,680
and he understands love.

103
00:05:58,199 --> 00:05:59,079
Now it's

104
00:06:00,439 --> 00:06:01,079
good.

105
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:06,040
Li Feiyuan,

106
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,040
promise me.

107
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:12,720
Keep going.

108
00:06:42,839 --> 00:06:43,720
Where is Lu Zhiyu?

109
00:06:44,120 --> 00:06:45,680
He gave you a blood transfusion

110
00:06:46,879 --> 00:06:47,439
when you were

111
00:06:48,319 --> 00:06:49,160
unconscious.

112
00:06:54,399 --> 00:06:54,959
Hao,

113
00:06:55,399 --> 00:06:56,360
how's she doing?

114
00:06:59,199 --> 00:06:59,800
She woke up.

115
00:07:01,160 --> 00:07:02,839
She woke up after being shot?

116
00:07:03,560 --> 00:07:05,199
The fish that took the bait have escaped.

117
00:07:05,959 --> 00:07:06,920
You bunch of useless idiots!

118
00:07:07,199 --> 00:07:08,560
Young Master Xie is always around.

119
00:07:08,680 --> 00:07:09,360
Our people

120
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:10,439
have no chance to intervene.

121
00:07:11,439 --> 00:07:12,519
This ungrateful wretch!

122
00:07:14,759 --> 00:07:15,199
Wait,

123
00:07:16,680 --> 00:07:18,000
Jiang Yue

124
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:20,920
shouldn't have woken up.

125
00:07:21,040 --> 00:07:22,600
The one with the compatible blood type

126
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,040
is right by her side.

127
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:38,240
Your temperature is rising,

128
00:07:38,759 --> 00:07:40,000
so you feel cold.

129
00:07:42,199 --> 00:07:43,439
42 degrees.

130
00:07:44,079 --> 00:07:45,240
Like having a fever.

131
00:07:47,160 --> 00:07:47,920
You'll get used to it.

132
00:07:58,160 --> 00:07:59,000
My blood

133
00:08:00,279 --> 00:08:01,240
flows my blood.

134
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,199
The resonance of the brand is more intense.

135
00:08:52,919 --> 00:08:55,279
What nonsense are you thinking about in your head?

136
00:08:55,720 --> 00:08:57,080
That's the scene you've imagined.

137
00:08:57,960 --> 00:08:59,279
It's just that I can sense it too.

138
00:09:02,600 --> 00:09:04,240
Just an old-fashioned spring dream.

139
00:09:08,519 --> 00:09:09,759
Don't pry into others' privacy.

140
00:09:11,320 --> 00:09:12,840
Your punches hurt especially now.

141
00:09:19,720 --> 00:09:20,600
Should we

142
00:09:20,720 --> 00:09:22,360
make some chicken soup for My Lord?

143
00:09:24,919 --> 00:09:25,799
Or brown sugar water?

144
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,120
Donkey-hide gelatin.

145
00:09:30,799 --> 00:09:32,720
It's the most effective in TV series.

146
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:34,600
Right?

147
00:09:38,159 --> 00:09:38,639
My brother.

148
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:40,000
I'm sorry.

149
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:42,120
It's my fault and Li Si's.

150
00:09:45,679 --> 00:09:46,240
Where's A Che?

151
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:47,480
He left.

152
00:09:48,399 --> 00:09:49,000
Again?

153
00:09:50,000 --> 00:09:50,639
My brother.

154
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,240
He's not a child.

155
00:09:52,799 --> 00:09:54,799
He won't be kidnapped.

156
00:09:55,679 --> 00:09:57,360
He won't make trouble.

157
00:09:58,919 --> 00:10:00,759
I'm just worried that he will get into trouble.

158
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:01,399
So...

159
00:10:03,840 --> 00:10:04,480
It's so hot.

160
00:10:05,360 --> 00:10:06,559
Give me some water.

161
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,080
Li Si,

162
00:10:17,639 --> 00:10:18,639
what are you doing?

163
00:10:19,799 --> 00:10:20,679
I just want to know

164
00:10:21,080 --> 00:10:22,279
if you get stronger

165
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,480
after getting My Lord's blood.

166
00:10:24,360 --> 00:10:25,879
You two hurt me the same.

167
00:10:35,879 --> 00:10:37,519
I'll go find a sandbag to practice.

168
00:10:49,080 --> 00:10:49,600
Where's A Che?

169
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:51,200
Go get him back.

170
00:10:51,440 --> 00:10:51,960
Yes.

171
00:11:02,480 --> 00:11:02,960
My Lord,

172
00:11:03,360 --> 00:11:04,360
we didn't find A Che,

173
00:11:04,879 --> 00:11:06,679
but we caught a henchman of Qin Yeren.

174
00:11:07,279 --> 00:11:09,399
He said that his Young Mistress ran away from home,

175
00:11:09,559 --> 00:11:10,320
and he was looking for her.

176
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,159
Qin Yaxin?

177
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:12,360
Yes.

178
00:11:13,240 --> 00:11:14,320
She wanted to marry you

179
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,960
to turn hostility into friendship.

180
00:11:16,639 --> 00:11:17,879
She quarreled with Qin Yeren,

181
00:11:18,360 --> 00:11:19,240
and ran away from home.

182
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:20,639
She also said that

183
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,200
there is no man she wants

184
00:11:22,279 --> 00:11:23,279
that she can't get.

185
00:11:27,919 --> 00:11:28,799
Tell Qin Yeren

186
00:11:29,559 --> 00:11:30,320
I want to see him.

187
00:11:39,120 --> 00:11:40,000
Boss Ah Ren.

188
00:11:41,240 --> 00:11:42,159
Long time no see.

189
00:11:46,159 --> 00:11:47,120
Are you investigating me?

190
00:11:48,759 --> 00:11:49,320
What's wrong?

191
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,840
I used to sell fish.

192
00:11:52,679 --> 00:11:53,440
It's not shameful.

193
00:11:54,519 --> 00:11:55,480
I see.

194
00:11:56,639 --> 00:11:58,200
I thought you were just coincidentally named that.

195
00:11:58,879 --> 00:11:59,559
Get to the point.

196
00:12:00,120 --> 00:12:00,600
Fine.

197
00:12:01,120 --> 00:12:02,200
Let's talk about the past.

198
00:12:03,519 --> 00:12:04,519
Sixteen years ago,

199
00:12:05,039 --> 00:12:06,840
a mother and daughter came to eat here.

200
00:12:07,240 --> 00:12:08,399
Too many customers.

201
00:12:08,559 --> 00:12:09,559
I don't remember.

202
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,240
You may not remember the mother,

203
00:12:12,000 --> 00:12:13,639
but you definitely remember the daughter.

204
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:15,639
Two days ago,

205
00:12:17,039 --> 00:12:18,399
you even tried to kill her.

206
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:21,679
16 years ago,

207
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:23,480
a woman named Jiang Jie came to investigate

208
00:12:23,919 --> 00:12:26,159
the news of wild wolves in the village.

209
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:30,399
The news said

210
00:12:30,759 --> 00:12:33,000
she rented a boat from you to go whale watching at sea,

211
00:12:33,879 --> 00:12:35,000
and drowned in a storm

212
00:12:35,559 --> 00:12:36,440
in the middle of the night.

213
00:12:44,240 --> 00:12:45,960
Are you blaming me for a natural disaster?

214
00:12:47,240 --> 00:12:47,919
Unfortunately,

215
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,759
I was also eating at your place that day.

216
00:12:52,440 --> 00:12:53,559
You told her

217
00:12:53,919 --> 00:12:55,759
about the whale migration route nearby.

218
00:12:56,440 --> 00:12:57,759
You have no reason to do this.

219
00:12:59,320 --> 00:12:59,919
Tell me,

220
00:13:01,480 --> 00:13:03,840
who's behind all this?

221
00:13:05,879 --> 00:13:07,080
Are you out of your mind?

222
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,159
This is my turf.

223
00:13:10,159 --> 00:13:11,960
Who can order me around?

224
00:13:13,279 --> 00:13:14,120
Over a decade ago,

225
00:13:14,200 --> 00:13:15,120
you were just a little brat.

226
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,399
What could you possibly remember?

227
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,600
Even if you recall something,

228
00:13:19,600 --> 00:13:20,399
who would believe you?

229
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,159
Do you believe me?

230
00:13:23,679 --> 00:13:24,360
Do you believe me?

231
00:13:24,799 --> 00:13:26,039
Do you believe me?

232
00:13:26,960 --> 00:13:28,320
Messing around in my turf,

233
00:13:30,159 --> 00:13:31,279
you're still too young.

234
00:14:36,279 --> 00:14:37,320
I'll give you two choices.

235
00:14:37,799 --> 00:14:38,360
First,

236
00:14:38,919 --> 00:14:40,960
tell me who the employer is.

237
00:14:41,039 --> 00:14:41,399
Second,

238
00:14:42,360 --> 00:14:43,399
die here.

239
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:44,919
You two,

240
00:14:46,840 --> 00:14:47,840
what are you doing?

241
00:14:48,320 --> 00:14:49,200
Young Master Xie.

242
00:14:50,600 --> 00:14:51,679
What a coincidence.

243
00:14:52,279 --> 00:14:53,240
Are you here

244
00:14:53,720 --> 00:14:55,480
for a negotiation or a brawl?

245
00:14:56,399 --> 00:14:57,799
If it's the latter,

246
00:14:58,919 --> 00:14:59,960
I won't get involved.

247
00:15:00,639 --> 00:15:01,840
Old friends catching up.

248
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:03,440
My car broke down.

249
00:15:04,600 --> 00:15:05,320
Give me a ride.
